'yabb252' => 'Jon Baker, Derek Barnstorm, Carsten Dalgaard, John G.D. McCabe, D.A. Rorabaugh.<br />Included Mods in YaBB 2.5.2 written by Derek Barnstorm, Carsten Dalgaard, and D.A. Rorabaugh.<br /><br />Dedicated to the memory of Ron Hartendorp, AKA Spikecity. He left us too soon.',
'yabb260' => 'Jon Baker, Derek Barnstorm, Carsten Dalgaard, John G.D. McCabe, George Nakos, D.A. Rorabaugh.<br />Included Mods in YaBB 2.6 written by AstroPilot, Derek Barnstorm, Carsten Dalgaard, and D.A. Rorabaugh with additional code and Mods from the YaBB 3.0 Development Team. We would be nowhere without the contributions of Mod-writers.',
